data.description: This friendly neighborhood home has lots to offer! It features a heated and cooled home office that you could also use for your man cave or she shed. Also being renovated a few years ago, it has LVP flooring throughout the home with new light fixtures. The builder of this one owner home took no shortcuts, the crawl space is insulated with foam boards and took extra protection against radon with the covered floor. Don't miss out on this highly desired neighborhood home.
